<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/670197-are-there-any-sex-scenes-in-this-book-i">Are there any sex scenes in this book? I am looking for a book by Michael Connelly or Grisham which has no sex in it for my son.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_670197'><a id="like_count_community_question_670197" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/670197?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">5 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F32508.The_Black_Echo">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/670197-are-there-any-sex-scenes-in-this-book-i">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/670197-are-there-any-sex-scenes-in-this-book-i">See all 8 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

