<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">You can read anyone and enjoy he has like 21 Harry Bosch books. I just went back and started at 1 and enjoyed reading them all again up the present. H<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">You can read anyone and enjoy he has like 21 Harry Bosch books. I just went back and started at 1 and enjoyed reading them all again up the present. Harry Bosch on Amazon tv takes parts from some of his books and uses them for the plots. He only uses parts and sometimes takes parts from a couple of books in one episode. All very good. All books and all 4 seasons very enjoyable <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
